tion: Author. Sneaking up from behind! Colorectal Cancer In Those Less Than The Screening Age. NZ Gastroenterology Society Conference, Wellington, New Zealand. November 2019.</span></li>\n<li><span>Poster: Author. Outcomes Of patients with Delayed Surveillance Colonoscopies: A Large Cohort Study in Tauranga, New Zealand. Digestive Disease Week, San Diego, USA. May 2019.</span></li>\n</ul><p><strong><span>2018</span></strong></p><ul>\n<li><span>Presentation, Speaker: Janssen No Honorarium Speaker on Therapeutic Drug Monitoring for anti-TNFs and thiopurines in New Zealand. Auckland, New Zealand. November 2018.</span></li>\n<li><span>Presentation, Speaker : Video or verbal? A randomised trial of the informed consent process prior to endoscopy. NZ Gastroenterology Society Conference, Dunedin, New Zealand. November 2018. Winner of New Zealand Gastroenterology Society ASM Young Investigator of the Year </span></li>\n<li><span>Presentation, Speaker: Surveillance factors change outcomes in patients with hepatocellular carcinoma due to chronic hepatitis C virus infection in New Zealand. NZ Gastroenterology Society Conference, Dunedin, New Zealand. November 2018.</span></li>\n<li><span>Poster, Author. Outcomes Of patients with Delayed Surveillance Colonoscopies: A Large Cohort Study in Tauranga, New Zealand. Winner of Poster Prize, NZ Gastroenterology Society Conference, Dunedin, New Zealand. November 2018.</span></li>\n<li><span>Poster, Author: Pan-Depressed Disaccharidase Levels As a Rare Cause for Unexplained Gastrointestinal Symptoms. NZ Gastroenterology Society Conference, Dunedin, New Zealand. November 2018.</span></li>\n<li><span>Poster, Author: High Rates Of Disaccharidase Enzyme Deficiency In Waitemata, Auckland. NZ Gastroenterology Society Conference, Dunedin, New Zealand. November 2018.</span></li>\n<li><span>Poster, Author. A successful novel algorithm to manage undifferentiated chronic diarrhoea with empirical therapy. NZ Gastroenterology Society Conference, Dune