(364, 6, 12, 0, 0, 1, 3, 0, 'SilverStripe\\Lessons\\PatientInformationPage', '2021-01-22 18:47:29', '2020-12-29 17:14:01', NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 'patient-information', 'Patient Information', NULL, '<p><br>Patient Information<br>Colonoscopy Bowel Preparation<br>The bowel must be completely empty before your colonoscopy so that the risk of lesions being<br>missed is minimised. This can be achieved by following the instructions below in the attached PDF.</p><p>Colonoscopy Bowel Preparation.pdf</p><p>Colonoscopy Low Fibre Diet<br>A low fibre diet reduces the volume of your bowel movements, which helps with adequate cleansing of your bowel prior to colonoscopy.<br>Please follow the food guide in the attached PDF.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 2, 0, 0, NULL, 0),
